pher go for the gold for free by utilizing free trials fromFuboTVandDirecTV Stream, or you can check out promotional offers fromSling TV.\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The event will also stream onPeacock, which offers a premium monthly subscription for$7.99/monthor a premium annual subscription for$79.99/year, where you can save 17% off in one payment.\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Christopher, who was born in Hartville, Ohio, qualified for the finals with the second-best score in the competition on Tuesday, earning 89.48 points.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hartville,_Ohio\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hartville, Ohio\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hartville,_Ohio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hartville,_Ohio\"}, {\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hartville,_Ohio\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hartville, Ohio\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hartville,_Ohio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hartville,_Ohio\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fellow American Justin Dowell nabbed fourth with 89.07 points while Britain's Kieran Reilly took the top qualifying mark with 91.68 points.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Institute_of_Electrical_and_Electronics_Engineers\", \"score\": 0.9997766207975008, \"rank\": 0.00019057510199751716, \"text\": \"Fellow\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Institute_of_Electrical_and_Electronics_Engineers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Institute_of_Electrical_and_Electronics_Engineers\"}, {\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9974711525714691, \"rank\": 0.0025308754772574472, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Dowell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Justin Dowell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Dowell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Dowell\"}, {\"begin\": 1119, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9895132880973228, \"rank\": 0.01059164558532658, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1129, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\", \"score\": 0.999967480608016, \"rank\": 3.2429196728709546e-05, \"text\": \"Kieran\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will be nine competitors in the finale as they navigate two final runs at the park.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Lake High School grad tallied 90.10 points in the first run, followed by an 88.87 in the second.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The journey has been an arduous one for the American.\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1428, \"end\": 1436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9974711525714691, \"rank\": 0.0025308754772574472, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He overcame a broken jaw and cheekbone at X Games 2023 to qualify for Paris.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999715610106, \"rank\": 2.843918648610111e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, he is one event away from his first medal at the Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BMX freestyle riding made its competitive debut in Tokyo at the 2020 games.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1638, \"end\": 1643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9973938944406731, \"rank\": 0.0022616040084462784, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's more information on how to watch Marcus Christopher today at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1704, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\", \"score\": 0.9605525573362654, \"rank\": 0.0410674484666312, \"text\": \"Marcus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's more information onChristopher's strong showing in qualifying on Tuesdayfrom writer Ed Klajman, special to cleveland.com.\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PARIS - Marcus Christopher's goal of taking home an Olympic medal is well within sight, after qualifying second in BMX Freestyle, with the final set for Wednesday night.\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1885, \"end\": 1891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\", \"score\": 0.9605525573362654, \"rank\": 0.0410674484666312, \"text\": \"Marcus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\"}, {\"begin\": 1992, \"end\": 1995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999995704311927, \"rank\": 4.233138944580036e-07, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Lake High School grad scored 90.10 on his first run, followed by 88.87 on his second, for an average of 89.48.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel great right now, I landed two runs,\\\" said the 21-year-old.\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It (the course) is big with a lot of ramps.\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was a little nervous with the heat, because I do not do good in the heat.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2351, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I hydrated a lot, and I felt better than I thought I was going to feel at the end of my run.\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I am ready to go for tomorrow, hopefully land a run and get a medal.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the plan.\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bring it on.\\\"\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Christopher, whose father Matt was a linebacker at Ohio State, added that he expects to bring his performance up to a whole new level in the final.\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2605, \"end\": 2615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio_State_Buckeyes\", \"score\": 0.8436876832400895, \"rank\": 0.1841964029503304, \"text\": \"Ohio State\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio_State_Buckeyes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ohio_State_Buckeyes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My whole run's going to be all different tricks, pretty much,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's all according to a plan.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I might switch a trick here and there on the fly (if I need to), but it's mainly all a plan.\\\"\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Christopher's score was only surpassed by the 91.21 registered by British rival Kieran Reilly, who will be very tough to beat, the American insisted.\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 3051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2968, \"end\": 2975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.997128317902333, \"rank\": 0.00275497543676378, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2982, \"end\": 2988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\", \"score\": 0.999967480608016, \"rank\": 3.2429196728709546e-05, \"text\": \"Kieran\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kieran_Culkin\"}, {\"begin\": 3033, \"end\": 3041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9974711525714691, \"rank\": 0.0025308754772574472, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He killed it (today).\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's been killing it these past few years and he's looking good.\\\"\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Christoper started riding a bike when he was four years old, tried freestyle when he was nine, and turned professional at 13.\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He finished ranked in the top four in the world in both 2022 and 2023, and earlier this season won a gold medal in at the X Games in California, with a score of 95.66, nearly five points ahead of second place.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3402, \"end\": 3412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Golden_Bears\", \"score\": 0.7222724591327203, \"rank\": 0.377972342565596, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Golden_Bears\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California_Golden_Bears\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That came after suffering a broken jaw and cheekbone, requiring multiple plates and screws, when appearing in the X Games one year earlier.\", \"from\": 3479, \"to\": 3618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He took second place at the Olympic Qualifier Series in Budapest this spring to qualify for Paris, scoring 92.98 in that competition.\", \"from\": 3620, \"to\": 3753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3676, \"end\": 3684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999948836811117, \"rank\": 5.112037624024352e-06, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 3712, \"end\": 3717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999715610106, \"rank\": 2.843918648610111e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbped